resources.string:
The main activity is used as a Now Playing Screen. Here the user will have to all the media buttons(Previews, Next, Play and Pause. The buttons will be ImageButtons and a OnClickListener  will change the background source for the pause/play each time it is clicked (setImageResource(...);
    \nFor all the activities the MediaCotroller class has to be used as it allows an app to interact with an ongoing media session. Media buttons and other commands ca be sent to the session.
    \nFurthermore the MediaPlayer class has to be used to play the audio.
